'''Aldin Gurdijeljac''' ([[Serbian Cyrillic]]: A<U+043B><U+0434><U+0438><U+043D> <U+0413><U+0443>p<U+0434><U+0438>je<U+0459>a<U+0446>; born 7 January 1978 in [[Novi Pazar]]) is a [[Serbia]]n-born [[Bosnia]]n [[Association football|football]] defender currently playing with [[KS Shkumbini Peqin]] in [[Albanian Superliga]].

He had previously played with [[FK Novi Pazar]], [[OFK Belgrade]] and [[FK Metalac Kraljevo]].

He holds both Serbian and Bosnian nationality.

